1. *Travu* sam juče kosio u dvorištu. (I mowed *the grass* in the yard yesterday.)
2. U proleće obično *trava* brzo raste. (In spring, *grass* usually grows quickly.)
3. Šetao sam se po *travi* i uživao u prirodi. (I walked on *the grass* and enjoyed nature.)
4. Ova livada je puna *trave*. (This meadow is full of *grass*.)
5. Sveže *trave* ima u bašti. (There is fresh *grass* in the garden.)
6. Nekoliko *trava* u mom vrtu još uvek nije izraslo. (A few *grasses* in my garden have not yet grown.)
7. Sadiću nove vrste *trave* u proleće. (I will plant new types of *grass* in the spring.)
8. Prolaznici su bacali smeće po *travi* pored puta. (Passersby were littering on *the grass* next to the road.)
9. Konj je pasao *travu* na livadi. (The horse was grazing *grass* in the meadow.)
10. Zelena *trava* me uvek podseća na leto. (Green *grass* always reminds me of summer.)